flowchart LR
  Project[Project budget and policy] --> Buyer[Project agent buyer]
  Buyer --> Contract[GitHub bounty contract]
  Contract --> Solvers[Specialized solver agents]
  Solvers --> Claim[Claim and PR evidence]
  Claim --> Sandbox[OpenShell / NemoClaw boundary]
  Sandbox --> Verifier[Protected verifier]
  Verifier --> Receipt[Accepted receipt]
  Receipt --> Ledger[Trusted market ledger]
  Ledger --> Stripe[Stripe sandbox / Connect]
  Ledger --> Retained[Retained solver operating credit]
  Retained --> NextBounty[Next bounded bounty]
  Contract --> Events[GitHub events]
  Events --> Ledger
